Well, Trillanes have shown everybody the evidence/proof of his accusation 
against Duterte. You said it was 'fake'. Not Duterte. That's the problem. 
You know more than Duterte. : )

Now, if Trillanes is producing fake documents, you think he is not 
answerable under the law? 

Duterte will just answer Trillanes' accusation? Well, that is really what 
Duterte's camp is doing. Answering, not really defending and challenging 
Trillanes to destroy and disprove his allegations. A very weak position 
even if I'm not a lawyer. 

You don't just answer nor dispute, you challenge and advance by filing 
counter suit to protect your person and reputation against malicious 
insinuation. 

Common sense dictates you don't have to have a lawyer or ask one to do 
those things. : )

accusation not Duterte to file a case disputing Trillanes claims...Ask a 
lawyer so that you will be enlightened

Anyway, the allegation is out in the open. Mayor Duterte has to address it 
IF he values his reputation. If he ignores it, there will be consequences 
which will complicate things. 

I say, if he is innocent, challenge Trillanes. Go to court file a case. 
Produce his counter evidence to dispute or discredit Trillanes evidence. 
Challenge him in an open public debate, etc. 

He can do a lot of things than hide behind lawyers and spokesperson. It's 
un-Duterte. Really. : 0

for discussion with regards to this matter..

reputation if he is clean.

Even if 1,000 angels says that Duterte is corrupt, has a secret bank

I have no doubt in Senate hearings but we all know that every time there is 
a Senate hearing there's accusation of playing politics. We all know that. 

What Trillanes is doing right now is actually fair because he's not doing 
it under the security of the Senate procedure. He's exposing himself to 
counter charges from Duterte which unfortunately is not taking advantage by 
filing a case against him. 

The Duterte camp, instead of coming strong against Trillanes, is dragging 
its feet by asking this (affidavit) or that or requesting this or that, 
etc. 

It really doesn't make sense. If I'm the one accused of corruption and I'm 
innocent, i'm not going to take it sitting down. Immediately I will file a 
case against the person. Kesehoda na mangyari. Giyera kung giyera. 
Makikipagpatayan ako sa reputation ko.
